Hmm.

33:50.548 --> 33:54.724
For a girl her age, that song seems
a little incredibly inappropriate.

33:54.927 --> 33:57.180
- Yeah.
- Very incredibly.

34:02.059 --> 34:04.528
Next is Emma Gale.

34:04.729 --> 34:07.983
Has anyone cleaned
this microphone recently?

34:08.190 --> 34:12.786
- Like an hour ago?
- Unbelievable. Are we savages?

34:40.056 --> 34:43.856
Oh, my gosh, she is amazing.
Are you Emma's parents?

34:44.060 --> 34:48.110
Hey, Mike and Meg Gale, pleased
to meet you. Boy, isn't she terrific?

34:48.313 --> 34:50.442
I think she's got a good
shot at winning.

34:50.650 --> 34:51.902
Well, we sure hope so.

34:52.109 --> 34:55.158
Without that prize money
the bank's going to take our farm.

34:55.362 --> 34:57.832
- Oh, that's terrible.
- Yeah.

34:58.032 --> 35:03.289
It's been in our family for five generations.
Mike's grandparents are buried there.

35:05.956 --> 35:08.880
So, uh, what are you two gonna do
with the money if you win?

35:09.043 --> 35:11.842
Uh, just nothing really, just...
I don't know.

35:12.004 --> 35:15.850
Um, could use some new seat covers
for the van.

35:16.008 --> 35:19.353
Um, possibly a hat.

35:21.555 --> 35:24.479
- Hey there.
- Fantastic, heh.

35:24.684 --> 35:26.903
I know we were
a little unprepared before...

35:27.103 --> 35:29.697
...but now we have
got the act for you.

35:29.897 --> 35:31.069
Yeah.

35:32.191 --> 35:34.819
We are, hold for it...

35:35.027 --> 35:36.745
...contortionists.

35:37.488 --> 35:38.785
Ta-da.

35:38.948 --> 35:41.792
All right, well,
let's see what you got.

35:48.958 --> 35:52.838
You might wanna go help your friends. They've
gotten themselves a little tangled, heh.

35:53.045 --> 35:55.173
Fantastic.

35:55.381 --> 35:59.682
We need aspirin,
a chiropractor and some baby oil.

35:59.885 --> 36:01.512
Right now.

36:02.221 --> 36:04.064
Okay.

36:05.099 --> 36:07.397
Next up, Lotte Lavoie.

36:07.601 --> 36:11.322
All right, all right. Throat spray.

36:38.424 --> 36:40.768
Who did this to me? Who?

36:40.968 --> 36:46.520
Someone is going to pay for this.
Someone is going to pay!

36:46.724 --> 36:49.728
Her throat has been sprayed
with some kind of chemical irritant.

36:49.935 --> 36:53.189
There's no permanent damage, but you
won't be able to sing for a week.

36:53.397 --> 36:56.367
I'm gonna sue you. And you.

36:56.525 --> 36:59.404
And you.
And everyone!

36:59.612 --> 37:05.836
Somebody had better fix this
or I am going to get mad!

37:07.161 --> 37:09.664
So do you think maybe
the Phantom is behind this?

37:09.830 --> 37:11.548
Hmm. It could be.

37:11.749 --> 37:15.424
We're behind schedule, people.
Next up are Blake and Jones.

37:15.628 --> 37:17.926
Okay, we'll keep an eye open
for the Phantom.

37:18.631 --> 37:20.474
Don't worry about a thing.

